'''HNLMS ''Pieter de Bitter''''' was a {{sclass|Jan van Amstel|minesweeper||ship}} of the [[Royal Netherlands Navy]] that served in [[World War II]].

==Service history==
''Pieter de Bitter'' was [[Scuttling|scuttled]] at [[Surabaya]] on 6 March 1942.

